{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/dynamic-email-template","result":{"data":{"projectsJson":{"title":"Dynamic Email Template","descriptionLong1":"I first worked with members of the marketing team to determine what features the template needed to have (product grids, hero image, call to action, etc.). I then built dynamic components for each element that are populated by the email list data file. Some of the components have logic built in (for showing different numbers of products, different logos, etc.).","descriptionLong2":"This template eliminated the need for one-off manually coded emails, which drastically increased the efficiency of our marketing team.","descriptionLong3":null,"descriptionShort":"This email template was built using Acoustic to enable marketers to build robust emails without developer support.","projectLink":null,"projectLinkText":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.872093023255814,"src":"/static/80a3966657984ebd8bfeb466425751e0/278a8/AHR-dynamic-email-template.jpg","srcSet":"/static/80a3966657984ebd8bfeb466425751e0/58301/AHR-dynamic-email-template.jpg 300w,\n/static/80a3966657984ebd8bfeb466425751e0/c61e4/AHR-dynamic-email-template.jpg 600w,\n/static/80a3966657984ebd8bfeb466425751e0/278a8/AHR-dynamic-email-template.jpg 1043w","sizes":"(max-width: 1043px) 100vw, 1043px"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"dynamic-email-template"}}}